---
layout: base.njk
title: LifeWatch Slovenia
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <h1 class="eyebrow">{{ home.hero.eyebrow }}</h1>
      <p>{{ home.hero.text }}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-media">
      <img src="{{ home.hero.image }}" alt="Illustrated map of Slovenia representing its biodiversity">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="feature-banner">
  <a href="{{ home.featureBanner.url }}">
    <img src="{{ home.featureBanner.image }}" alt="">
  </a>
</section>

<section class="home-section resources">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>Resources & Services</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="resource-grid">
    {% for item in home.resources %}
      <a class="resource-card" href="{{ item.url }}">
        <span class="resource-icon"><img src="{{ item.icon }}" alt=""></span>
        <span class="resource-title">{{ item.title }}</span>
        <strong class="resource-count" data-resource-type="{{ item.metadataType }}">{{ item.count }}</strong>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  <a class="button" href="https://metadata.izrk.zrc-sazu.si/">Open Metadata Portal</a>
</section>

<section class="eric-kicker">
  <h3>We are part of <strong>LifeWatch ERIC</strong>, the e-Science infrastructure</h3>
  <h3>for research on biodiversity and ecosystems.</h3>
</section>

<section class="split-section">
  <div class="split-inner">
    <div class="about-image" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="about-copy">
      <h2>LifeWatch ERIC</h2>
      <p>LifeWatch ERIC facilitates the sharing and aggregation of open data and its integration and analysis through advanced modeling tools. Its VREs, together with computing capacity and the most innovative technologies, allow for testing scenarios of change in the organization and conservation of biodiversity, ecosystems and their services in response to different pressures.</p>
      <div class="about-spacer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <h2>LifeWatch Slovenia</h2>
      <p>Slovenian researchers cooperating in this infrastructure are seeking to raise Slovenian science to an internationally comparable level in Environmental<br>sciences.</p>
      <p>LifeWatch is part of the Slovenian Strategy for Smart Specialization<br>(S4) and Horizon 2020, focusing on the development of technological solu-<br>tions in the field of biodiversity and socio-ecosystem research.</p>
      <p>Since 2015, the Slovenian Consortium, LifeWatch-SI, has been promoting<br>the importance of integrating and networking information &amp; data in order to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>coordinate biodiversity research in marine, freshwater and terrestrial eco-<br>systems;</li>
        <li>plan common access to a vast array of data from various databases and<br>observatories;</li>
        <li>predict computing capabilities with analytical and modelling tools in virtual<br>laboratories;</li>
        <li>support training and educational programs that will enable a proper under-<br>standing of biodiversity</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-section projects">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>Projects</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="project-grid">
    {% for project in home.projects %}
      <article class="project-card">
        <a class="project-image" href="{{ project.url }}"><img src="{{ project.image }}" alt=""></a>
        <h3><a href="{{ project.url }}">{{ project.title }}</a></h3>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-section news-preview">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>News & Events</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="news-grid">
    {% for post in posts | limit(6) %}
      <article class="news-card">
        {% if post.image %}<img src="{{ post.image }}" alt="">{% endif %}
        <div>
          <h3><a href="/{{ post.slug }}/">{{ post.title | safe }}</a></h3>
          <p class="post-meta"><time datetime="{{ post.date }}">{{ post.date | wordpressDate }}</time><span>No Comments</span></p>
          <p>{{ post.excerpt | safe }}</p>
          <a class="read-more" href="/{{ post.slug }}/">Read More &raquo;</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-section consortium">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>Consortium</h2>
    <p>The LifeWatch-SI consortium consists of 10 partners from nationally and internationally recognised scientific institutions, universities, a regional park, a national museum, and an NGO, all active in the field of biodiversity and ecosystem research, with ZRC SAZU serving as the national coordinator and headquarters of LifeWatch-SI.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="partner-grid">
    {% for partner in home.partners %}
      <a class="partner-card" href="{{ partner.url }}">
        <span class="partner-image"><img src="{{ partner.image }}" alt=""></span>
        <h3>{{ partner.title }}</h3>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
